<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idb6de0f77-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa" identifier="/us/usc/t42/s300mm–2"><num value="300mm–2">§ 300mm–2.</num><heading> Education and outreach</heading>
<chapeau style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The WTC Program Administrator shall institute a program that provides education and outreach on the existence and availability of services under the WTC Program. The outreach and education program—</chapeau><paragraph style="-uslm-lc:I12" class="indent1" id="idb6e07f78-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa" identifier="/us/usc/t42/s300mm–2/1"><num value="1">(1)</num><chapeau> shall include—</chapeau><subparagraph style="-uslm-lc:I13" class="indent2" id="idb6e07f79-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa" identifier="/us/usc/t42/s300mm–2/1/A"><num value="A">(A)</num><content> the establishment of a public Web site with information about the WTC Program;</content>
</subparagraph>
<subparagraph style="-uslm-lc:I13" class="indent2" id="idb6e07f7a-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa" identifier="/us/usc/t42/s300mm–2/1/B"><num value="B">(B)</num><content> meetings with potentially eligible populations;</content>
</subparagraph>
<subparagraph style="-uslm-lc:I13" class="indent2" id="idb6e07f7b-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa" identifier="/us/usc/t42/s300mm–2/1/C"><num value="C">(C)</num><content> development and dissemination of outreach materials informing people about the program; and</content>
</subparagraph>
<subparagraph style="-uslm-lc:I13" class="indent2" id="idb6e07f7c-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa" identifier="/us/usc/t42/s300mm–2/1/D"><num value="D">(D)</num><content> the establishment of phone information services; and</content>
</subparagraph>
</paragraph>
<paragraph style="-uslm-lc:I12" class="indent1" id="idb6e07f7d-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa" identifier="/us/usc/t42/s300mm–2/2"><num value="2">(2)</num><chapeau> shall be conducted in a manner intended—</chapeau><subparagraph style="-uslm-lc:I13" class="indent2" id="idb6e07f7e-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa" identifier="/us/usc/t42/s300mm–2/2/A"><num value="A">(A)</num><content> to reach all affected populations; and</content>
</subparagraph>
<subparagraph style="-uslm-lc:I13" class="indent2" id="idb6e07f7f-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa" identifier="/us/usc/t42/s300mm–2/2/B"><num value="B">(B)</num><content> to include materials for culturally and linguistically diverse populations.</content>
</subparagraph>
</paragraph>
<sourceCredit id="idb6e07f80-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa">(<ref href="/us/act/1944-07-01/ch373">July 1, 1944, ch. 373</ref>, title XXXIII, § 3303, as added <ref href="/us/pl/111/347/tI/s101">Pub. L. 111–347, title I, § 101</ref>, <date date="2011-01-02">Jan. 2, 2011</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/124/3629">124 Stat. 3629</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
</section>
